songs.title: Doo Wop Outro
songs.lyrics:
[Verse: DJ Doo Wop]
Hold up A, hold up man
I, I forgot to play this one joint before we get up outta here man
It's some crazy shit the streets will definitely love
And you know what I mean
My nigga gets in the ring with the best of them baby
This is how a legacy is built
Years of unadulterated verbal abuse on these motherfucking mics
AZ salute
Doo Wop I'm up out of here
I'ma leave you with this one though
Styles P what up
